properties.areaDesc: Delaware Bay waters south of East Point NJ to Slaughter Beach DE
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 18 at 4:10PM EST until January 20 at 6:00AM EST by NWS Mount Holly NJ
properties.description:
* WHAT...South to southwest wind 15 to 20 knots with gusts up to
25 knots from late today into tonight. West to northwest wind
20 to 25 knots with gusts up to 30 knots on Sunday and Sunday
night. Waves 3 to 5 feet are expected.

* WHERE...Delaware Bay waters south of East Point NJ to
Slaughter Beach DE.

* WHEN...Until 6 AM EST Monday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 6 AM EST MONDAY
